<p>&ldquo;Outbound Tour&rdquo; means a tour operated by FLP outside of India and includes, but is not limited to, brochure tours, special tours, packages, cruise, sightseeing, carnival, cosmos, star cruise etc.</p>
<p>&ldquo;Tour Cost&rdquo; means total booking cost of all the services booked by the User for his outbound tour.</p>
<p>&ldquo;Booking Fees&rdquo; means a non-refundable fee or token money deposited at the time of booking by the User.</p>
<p>&ldquo;Brochure&rdquo; means catalogue, leaflet, e-mail or any other document containing the details about the itinerary and activities on an outbound tour.</p>
<p>&ldquo;Infant&rdquo; means a person below the age of 2 years and child means a person above the age of 2 years and below the age of 12 years.</p>
