<p>In case of publication of any travel scheme offering any discount or benefit by FLP, FLP shall have the sole right to withdraw such a scheme or discount at any time.</p>
<p><strong><strong>Tour Arrangements &amp; Other Activities</strong></strong></p>
<p>For tour arrangements like carnival, cosmos, star cruise, amusement parks, museums etc., the terms and conditions specified by such respective entities shall also be applicable.</p>
